Ingredients 
- 24 cl corn meal
- 3/4 tsp salt
- 1 beaten egg
- 11.83 cl flour
- 1/2 tsp baking soda
- 24 cl buttermilk
- 2 tbsp shortening

Heat oven to 200Â°C
Put shortening in iron skillet for 10 minutes and heat while mixing batter
Mix remaining ingredients
Pour batter onto hot skillet
Bake 20-25 minutes (or until brown)
Turn over to broil for a few minutes



